flowRoot.flowPara: João Paulo Almeida currently is an admitted Ph.D. candidate in Computer Science, at the Federal University of Bahia, Salvador, Brazil. He received his M.Sc in Applied Computing and Computer Engineering degree from State University of Feira de Santana, Feira de Santana, Brazil. He has worked as Professor in Adventist college of Bahia, lectured in Database, Computer Architecture, and Operational Systems. His areas of interests are Semantic Web, Information Retrieval, Spatial Queries, and Databases.
